The Creator archetype channels the power of imagination, artistry, and
bold vision. It's all about self-expression, pushing boundaries, and
bringing something new and inspiring into the world. Creator brands feel
like artists excitedly sketching possibilities, dreamers shaping the
future, and innovators daring to reinvent what we know. They remind us
that we are not just consumers of reality but also its architects, free
to design and redesign at will.

[Example:] Home Depot, although counterintuitive, is a
Creator archetype. They help you bring your vision (new kitchen, deck)
to life.

## 2. Caregiver

**- Promise:** To Help Others.

**- Motto:** Love your neighbour as yourself.

**- AKA:** The protector, saint, altruist, parent, helper, supporter,
