## 6. Lover

**- Promise:** Connection.

**- Motto:** You\'re the only one.

**- AKA:** Passionate, intimate, sensualist, magnetic.

**- Lover brands:** Hallmark, Revlon, Guess Jeans, Calvin Klein,
